Description: # sphinxcontrib-apa
        
        Simple APA citation style for [Sphinx](https://www.sphinx-doc.org/) and [Juptyer Book](https://jupyterbook.org/).
        
        ## Open source notice
        
        This project is open to updates by its users, [I](https://github.com/jeanlescure) ensure that PRs are relevant to the community.
        In other words, if you find a bug or want a new feature, please help us by becoming one of the
        [contributors](#contributors-) ‚úåÔ∏è ! See the [contributing section](#contributing)
        
